# Performance Monitoring - Quick Reference Card

## ?? What It Does
Automatically measures and displays CPU performance of graphics algorithms in both **FAST** (instant) and **SLOW** (animated step-by-step) modes.

---

## ?? Display Metrics

Located on **right side** of window. Shows:

| Metric | What It Means | Example |
|--------|--------------|---------|
| **Time** | Execution duration | 8.76 ms (FAST) vs 125.43 ms (SLOW) |
| **CPU** | System CPU usage | 5.3% (FAST) vs 15.2% (SLOW) |
| **Memory** | Memory allocated | 0.001 MB |
| **Ratio** | Slow ÷ Fast | 14.31x (animation is 14x slower) |
| **CPU ?** | SLOW CPU - FAST CPU | +9.9% (animation uses 10% more CPU) |

