## ?? User Guide (5 minutes)

### Step 1: Run in FAST Mode
```
1. Make sure toggle checkbox is UNCHECKED (next to button)
2. Click any drawing button (e.g., button12 = DDA)
3. Algorithm draws instantly
4. View metrics on right side
```

### Step 2: Run in SLOW Mode
```
1. CHECK the toggle checkbox next to the button
2. Click the same drawing button
3. Watch step-by-step animation
4. Metrics update to show SLOW times
```

### Step 3: Compare
```
After running both FAST and SLOW:
- Look for "SLOW vs FAST Comparison" section
- Note the Ratio (how many times slower)
- Note the CPU ? (animation overhead)
```

### Step 4: Copy Results
```
Double-click the metrics label
Text copied to clipboard
Paste into email, document, etc.
```

