## ?? What to Expect

### Fast Mode (Toggle OFF)
- Execution time: **Small** (2-100 ms typically)
- CPU usage: **Low** (2-10%)
- Single screen update
- Result: **Instant** drawing

### Slow Mode (Toggle ON)
- Execution time: **Larger** (50 ms - many seconds)
- CPU usage: **Higher** (10-30%)
- Multiple screen updates (per step)
- Result: **Step-by-step** visible animation

### Example Numbers (DDA algorithm)
| Mode | Time | CPU | Ratio |
|------|------|-----|-------|
| FAST | 8.76 ms | 5.3% | 1.0x (baseline) |
| SLOW | 125.43 ms | 15.2% | 14.31x slower |

