## ?? Technical Specs

### Precision
- Time: **Microsecond** precision via Stopwatch
- CPU: **System-wide** measurement (Windows Performance Counter)
- Memory: **Differential** tracking (GC-based)

### Thread Safety
- ? All UI updates safe via Invoke()
- ? Stopwatch timing is atomic
- ? Dictionary access is isolated per algorithm

### Performance
- **Measurement overhead**: <5ms total
- **Memory per snapshot**: ~200 bytes
- **Storage limit**: Negligible (grows with runs)

### Graceful Degradation
- **CPU counter unavailable?** Shows 0% (continues to work)
- **Memory unavailable?** Shows 0 MB (continues to work)
- **No breaking changes** if monitoring disabled

