## ? FAQ

**Q: How do I clear old metrics?**
A: Restart the application (metrics are per-session)

**Q: Can I compare two different algorithms?**
A: Yes, use `PerformanceMonitor.GetSummaryReport()` in code

**Q: Why do times vary between runs?**
A: System load, garbage collection, CPU scheduling vary

**Q: How many times should I run each algorithm?**
A: 3+ times; take the average for consistency

**Q: What if metrics don't show?**
A: Scroll right if label is off-screen; check window width

**Q: Can I export metrics to Excel?**
A: Copy text from label, paste to Excel (future CSV export possible)

