## ?? Quick Commands

### For Students
- **See metrics**: Click button, look right
- **Compare modes**: Run with toggle OFF, then ON
- **Copy results**: Double-click metrics label

### For Instructors
- **Demonstrate**: Use projector, show FAST vs SLOW side-by-side
- **Analyze**: Call `PerformanceMonitor.GetSummaryReport()` in breakpoint
- **Document**: Copy metrics, paste into lesson materials

### For Developers
```csharp
// Get latest measurement
var latest = PerformanceMonitor.GetLatestSnapshot("DDA");

// Get all measurements
var all = PerformanceMonitor.GetMetrics("DDA");

// Compare modes
var comparison = PerformanceMonitor.GetPerformanceComparison("DDA");

// Get summary
var report = PerformanceMonitor.GetSummaryReport();

// Clear history
PerformanceMonitor.ClearMetrics("DDA");  // Just DDA
PerformanceMonitor.ClearMetrics();       // Everything
```

