## ?? Troubleshooting

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| Metrics label not visible | Resize window wider, label on right edge |
| Times seem very high | Might be in SLOW mode; check toggle |
| CPU always shows 0% | Performance counter unavailable (OK, system continues) |
| Results vary wildly | Run 3+ times and average; check system load |
| Copy doesn't work | Double-click label, not single-click |
| Algorithm doesn't measure | Verify algorithm has Begin/End wrapping |

